  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK354">
<l>aiyuṇar veytiyak kaṇṇum payamiṉṟē</l>
<l>meyyuṇar villā tavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even those who have all the knowledge which can be attained by the five senses, will derive no benefit from it, if they are without a knowledge of the true nature of things.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
